title: StarTalk Live! at the Apollo (Part 1)
description: It’s not your typical night at the Apollo when Neil deGrasse Tyson and Eugene Mirman welcome Senator Cory Booker, science evangelist Dr. Ainissa Ramirez and comedians Maeve Higgins and Phoebe Robinson to the historic theater in Harlem, NYC.
author: feed@startalkradio.net (Neil deGrasse Tyson)
